    "causal_summary": "111 per-scenario snippet FILENAMES under feature_catalog/<category>/ and manual_testing_playbook/<category>/ across 9 skill packets carry a zero-padded 3-digit NNN- ordinal prefix. The prefix is load-bearing in exactly one place — the deep-improvement Lane C skill-benchmark loader ingests a sk-doc-shape scenario only when its basename is 3-digit-prefixed — so stripping it blind would silently drop all 111 scenarios from the benchmark corpus.",
